Suggests: apt-transport-https
Description: Unified package manager for APT, Snap, and Flatpak
 Unified Package Manager (UPM) is a comprehensive graphical package manager
 for Zorin OS that unifies APT, Snap, and Flatpak package management in a
 single intuitive interface.
 .
 Features:
  * Search for applications across multiple repositories simultaneously
  * Install and uninstall packages with a single click
  * Manage APT, Snap, and Flatpak packages in one place
  * Configure repository access and preferences
  * View comprehensive logs of all operations
  * Export logs for debugging and record-keeping
 .
 This application is designed specifically for Zorin OS and Ubuntu-based
 distributions, providing a user-friendly alternative to command-line
 package management.
